{"tid":2404361,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[正視聽]用鬼機都係幫推安心出行","createTime":"2021-02-11T16:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T09:08:34.000Z","uid":113951,"like":47,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b27ed86e34532c356dd336ed491dadc90a978787","tid":2404361,"uid":113951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T16:04:36.000Z","msg":"應承我<br />\n用太空卡同鬼機冇用<br />\n千其唔好裝安心出行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n// 一些荒謬的習慣，能幫助極權政府維持統治。捷克劇作家和前總統哈維爾，在其經典著作&lt;無權者的權力&gt;中，講了一個士多老闆的小故事。<br />\n<br />\n士多老闆在鋪頭掛起了「全世界工人階級團結起來」橫額，人人都知這是廢話，包括他本人。但他得透過這種「儀式」去表態自己服從政權，了解遊戲規則。而極權就是透過無數這種人人都鳩做的表態「儀式」，去維持並彰顯其合法性。<br />\n<br />\n故此網上有人提出用另一部電話，或太空卡開機去掃瞄QR code，必須注意這反而可能是在幫助政府推行「安心出行」的整套荒謬邏輯。因為你表面上還是服從了規則，和接受了店員的無理檢查，給予它不適當的合法性，從而支持了整個「安心出行」機制運作。<br />\n<br />\n可以反其道而行，全民回歸石器時代，做個食古不化的技術保守主義者，去餐廳寫字登記，避免用養成方便的「健康碼」習慣，並對其他人宣示自己真係「好廢好古老 」，不識「安心出行」這些「高科技 」。//<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/60255480827875169ec6f842\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2Fblackmirrortech%2Fshow%2F60255480827875169ec6f842&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=e029bad1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/60255480827875169ec6f842</a>"},{"pid":"d65d84f24a538e911efc49b81251b7c66be2c1be","tid":2404361,"uid":113951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T16:19:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/k